1:
Do not be irritated because of evildoers;
\q do not be envious of those who act unrighteously.
\q

3:
Trust in Yahweh and do what is good;
\q settle in the land and graze in faithfulness.
\q

5:
Give your ways to Yahweh;
\q trust in him, and he will act on your behalf.
\q

22:
Those who are blessed by God will inherit the land;
\q those who are cursed by him will be cut off.
\q

31:
The law of his God is in his heart;
\q his feet will not slip.
\q

37:
Observe the man of integrity, and mark the upright;
\q there is a good future for a man of peace.
\q

39:
Salvation of the righteous comes from Yahweh;
\q he protects them in the times of trouble.
\q
